div.div:
feat: add comment functionality with CRUD operations
- Implemented comment handler and service for creating and listing comments. - Added new routes for comment management in the router. - Created comment repository for database interactions. - Updated configuration definitions to include new comment settings. - Enhanced the comment model to support nested comments and additional fields. - Integrated Gravatar settings into the comment system. - Updated go.mod and go.sum to include necessary dependencies for comment handling.

feat: implement comment system with fetching, posting, and replying functionalities
- Added API methods for fetching and creating comments. - Created PostComment component with form for submitting comments. - Implemented CommentItem component to display individual comments. - Added icons for actions like reply, like, and refresh. - Integrated user agent parsing to display device information in comments. - Enhanced styling for comment form and list for better user experience. - Included validation for email and website fields in the comment form.
chore: 更新子项目引用到新版本

feat: add Comment entity schema with fields and relationships
- Implemented Comment schema with fields for ID, timestamps, article/user relationships, and comment content. - Added support for soft deletes using SoftDeleteMixin. - Defined edges for article, user, and parent-child comment relationships. - Created indexes for efficient querying on article_id, status, parent_id, user_id, and email.
